{"title":"给吴科长（某机关的一张大字报）","authors":["袁心"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":12,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给吴科长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（某机关的一张大字报）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会计科，吴科长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办事稳健经验广。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提缺点，有两条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作被动占主要。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考虑多，决定少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕出错误受不了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇见事，问领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咋说咋办责任小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再就是，脾气躁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科内团结没做好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈问题，欠沉着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批评工作更是少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对不对？别生气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改进作风要积极！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}